30
00:02:09,674 --> 00:02:13,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I, uh...</b></font>

31
00:02:24,224 --> 00:02:27,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, did you get the day off today?</b></font>

32
00:02:31,764 --> 00:02:33,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi?</b></font>

33
00:02:33,734 --> 00:02:36,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry to bother you at work.</b></font>

34
00:02:36,734 --> 00:02:38,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's okay.</b></font>

35
00:02:38,304 --> 00:02:41,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What time do you get off work today?</b></font>

36
00:02:41,434 --> 00:02:42,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

37
00:02:42,934 --> 00:02:45,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm free the rest of the day,</b></font>

38
00:02:45,304 --> 00:02:50,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I thought maybe we could hang out.</b></font>

39
00:02:50,114 --> 00:02:54,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll wait somewhere until
