40
00:02:54,484 --> 00:02:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you hold on a sec?</b></font>

41
00:02:56,654 --> 00:03:00,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait here for two... one minute!</b></font>

42
00:03:00,954 --> 00:03:03,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey!
--Boss!</b></font>

43
00:03:04,064 --> 00:03:07,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm leaving early for personal reasons!</b></font>

44
00:03:07,694 --> 00:03:09,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck?!</b></font>

45
00:03:11,864 --> 00:03:15,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where are you going? Itsuki!</b></font>

46
00:03:15,374 --> 00:03:17,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cover for me, Takumi!</b></font>

47
00:03:19,604 --> 00:03:22,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hop in, Kazumi!
--Is it really okay?</b></font>

48
00:03:22,414 --> 00:03:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, come on!</b></font>

49
00:03:31,724 --> 00:03:36,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess I'll give him a break just this once.</b></font>

50
00:03:36,224 --> 00:03:39,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is that girl? His new girlfriend?</b></font>

51
00:03:39,964 --> 00:03:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something like that.</b></font>

52
00:03:42,394 --> 00:03:46,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? He just got dumped.</b></font>

53
00:03:46,234 --> 00:03:48,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He got another girl already?</b></font>

54
00:03:48,604 --> 00:03:51,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened to the "Lonely Driver"?!</b></font>

55
00:03:51,904 --> 00:03:55,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure you can leave work like this?</b></font>

56
00:03:55,074 --> 00:03:56,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure.</b></font>

57
00:03:56,574 --> 00:03:59,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no big deal!</b></font>

58
00:03:59,444 --> 00:04:03,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My boss may get mad at me tomorrow...</i></b></font>

59
00:04:03,214 --> 00:04:05,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but I don't care!</i></b></font>

60
00:04:05,824 --> 00:04:09,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've been thinking about Kazumi all day.</i></b></font>

61
00:04:09,824 --> 00:04:13,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wanted to go see her so much.</i></b></font>

62
00:04:15,394 --> 00:04:19,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Knowing she decided to come see me...</i></b></font>

63
00:04:19,404 --> 00:04:22,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...made me so happy!</i></b></font>

64
00:04:22,434 --> 00:04:26,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So leaving work is no big deal.</i></b></font>

65
00:04:47,564 --> 00:04:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I was growing up, I always
hung out with my brother.</b></font>

66
00:04:51,864 --> 00:04:53,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

67
00:04:53,404 --> 00:04:55,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You two still seem very close.</b></font>

68
00:04:55,874 --> 00:04:58,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After he got into racing,</b></font>

69
00:04:58,374 --> 00:05:01,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd always go with him to his races.</b></font>

70
00:05:01,644 --> 00:05:03,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There was a time when I was using</b></font>

71
00:05:03,544 --> 00:05:06,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>most of my salary to maintain his car.</b></font>

72
00:05:06,714 --> 00:05:08,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

73
00:05:08,184 --> 00:05:11,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There was nothing I wanted to do.</b></font>

74
00:05:11,484 --> 00:05:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was easy to just follow
my car-crazed brother.</b></font>

75
00:05:15,494 --> 00:05:17,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's no good.</b></font>

76
00:05:17,994 --> 00:05:20,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He and I are two different people.</b></font>

77
00:05:20,864 --> 00:05:24,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to find out what I want to do.</b></font>

78
00:05:24,334 --> 00:05:25,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

79
00:05:30,504 --> 00:05:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unfortunately...</b></font>

80
00:05:32,004 --> 00:05:35,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...there's nothing I'm
passionate about right now.</b></font>

81
00:05:35,414 --> 00:05:38,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'll find out what my dream is.</b></font>

82
00:05:39,744 --> 00:05:44,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until now, I haven't had
anyone to talk to like this.</b></font>

83
00:05:44,084 --> 00:05:48,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I'm very glad I met you, Itsuki.</b></font>

84
00:05:48,094 --> 00:05:52,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, too! I'm very glad I met you, too!</b></font>

85
