<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

96
00:06:33,664 --> 00:06:35,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something happened at work today.</b></font>

97
00:06:35,874 --> 00:06:37,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened?</b></font>

98
00:06:39,044 --> 00:06:41,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have this mean co-worker</b></font>

99
00:06:41,874 --> 00:06:44,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who blames me for her mistakes</b></font>

100
00:06:44,544 --> 00:06:46,884
