101
00:06:46,884 --> 00:06:49,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's unbearable.</b></font>

102
00:06:49,554 --> 00:06:53,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right! I'll stay with you
until you feel better!</b></font>

103
00:06:53,754 --> 00:06:56,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For as long as it takes!</b></font>

104
