<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There!</b></font>

105
00:07:04,334 --> 00:07:07,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Steer while braking lightly.
--Okay.</b></font>

106
00:07:10,504 --> 00:07:12,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're good at this!</b></font>

107
00:07:12,244 --> 00:07:14,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it feels good!</b></font>

108
00:07:20,854 --> 00:07:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a better teacher than Takumi.</b></font>

109
00:07:24,084 --> 00:07:28,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother taught me things
while I sat next to him.</b></font>

110
00:07:28,094 --> 00:07:31,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They just stayed in my head.</b></font>

111
00:07:31,094 --> 00:07:36,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? I bet you'll be good at
this once you get your license.</b></font>

112
00:07:36,594 --> 00:07:38,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true.</b></font>

113
00:07:38,434 --> 00:07:40,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm all talk.</b></font>

114
00:07:40,874 --> 00:07:43,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't race a mountain pass myself.</b></font>

115
00:07:43,844 --> 00:07:46,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have to.</b></font>

116
00:07:46,104 --> 00:07:49,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's just one of the many
pleasures a car brings.</b></font>

117
00:07:49,044 --> 00:07:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should get your license.</b></font>

118
00:07:51,284 --> 00:07:55,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Driving will open up another world for you.</b></font>

119
00:07:55,884 --> 00:07:59,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you get your license at a driving school,</b></font>

120
00:07:59,224 --> 00:08:01,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it may lead you places.</b></font>

121
00:08:01,324 --> 00:08:03,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stepping on the gas</b></font>

122
00:08:03,324 --> 00:08:05,324
