123
00:08:05,324 --> 00:08:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can go anywhere you want.</b></font>

124
00:08:07,994 --> 00:08:10,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a lot of fun.</b></font>

125
00:08:20,644 --> 00:08:23,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

126
00:08:30,524 --> 00:08:33,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I absolutely can't lose to you.</b></font>

127
00:08:33,184 --> 00:08:36,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll settle this shortly.</b></font>

128
00:08:36,994 --> 00:08:41,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I probably can't avoid...</i></b></font>

129
00:08:41,364 --> 00:08:42,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...this race.</i></b></font>

130
00:08:55,174 --> 00:08:58,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you asleep, Itsuki?</b></font>

131
00:08:58,184 --> 00:08:59,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm not.</b></font>

132
00:08:59,614 --> 00:09:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was going to quit my job
and go back to Saitama.</b></font>

133
00:09:05,184 --> 00:09:08,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'll give it another try.</b></font>

134
00:09:10,564 --> 00:09:12,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Quitting is easy,</b></font>

135
00:09:12,994 --> 00:09:16,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'd just be back where I started.</b></font>

136
00:09:33,184 --> 00:09:35,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

137
00:09:35,354 --> 00:09:36,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki.</b></font>

138
00:09:36,854 --> 00:09:38,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If anyone asks,</b></font>

139
00:09:38,024 --> 00:09:40,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was hanging out with you</b></font>

140
00:09:40,184 --> 00:09:43,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>from last night until this morning, okay?</b></font>

141
00:09:43,894 --> 00:09:47,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! You just got back this morning?</b></font>

142
00:09:47,864 --> 00:09:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

143
00:09:49,264 --> 00:09:51,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Were you with Kazumi?</b></font>

144
00:09:51,834 --> 00:09:54,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

145
00:09:54,174 --> 00:09:56,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you blushing?!</b></font>

146
00:09:56,004 --> 00:09:58,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't get the wrong idea!</b></font>

147
00:09:58,174 --> 00:10:01,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We just went to the pass is all!</b></font>

148
00:10:01,014 --> 00:10:03,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We slept in my car.</b></font>

149
00:10:03,174 --> 00:10:05,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But isn't that improper?</b></font>

150
00:10:05,514 --> 00:10:07,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi is a girl.</b></font>

151
00:10:07,284 --> 00:10:11,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But she said she didn't
want to go home last night.</b></font>

152
00:10:11,384 --> 00:10:14,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a man's job to stay with his girl.</b></font>

153
00:10:14,894 --> 00:10:19,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it? I don't really know.</b></font>

154
00:10:19,094 --> 00:10:22,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was so happy yesterday.</b></font>

155
00:10:22,064 --> 00:10:24,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We talked about lots of things.</b></font>

156
00:10:24,604 --> 00:10:27,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It made us closer.</b></font>

157
00:10:27,134 --> 00:10:29,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was like a dream!</b></font>

158
00:10:31,274 --> 00:10:34,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, how about you?</b></font>

159
00:10:34,444 --> 00:10:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come to think of it,
Natsuki's been absent lately.</b></font>

160
00:10:39,384 --> 00:10:41,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is she sick?</b></font>

161
00:10:41,884 --> 00:10:44,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

162
00:10:44,554 --> 00:10:48,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't know? That's weird.</b></font>

163
00:11:03,334 --> 00:11:05,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dad?</b></font>

164
00:11:05,674 --> 00:11:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess he's out.</b></font>

165
00:11:08,274 --> 00:11:11,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

166
00:11:11,514 --> 00:11:12,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

167
00:11:12,714 --> 00:11:16,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're probably wondering
how I got your number.</b></font>

168
00:11:16,414 --> 00:11:19,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I remembered the
Fujiwara Tofu Shop emblem...</b></font>

169
00:11:19,584 --> 00:11:21,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...on your car.</b></font>

170
00:11:21,694 --> 00:11:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be coming to Gunma
tomorrow to get my sister.</b></font>

171
00:11:26,564 --> 00:11:29,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard she took off from work yesterday</b></font>

172
00:11:29,964 --> 00:11:32,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and didn't come back until this morning.</b></font>

173
00:11:32,434 --> 00:11:34,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So irresponsible!</b></font>

174
00:11:34,604 --> 00:11:39,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't stand irresponsible people,
even when it's my sister.</b></font>

175
00:11:39,204 --> 00:11:40,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Itsuki is in trouble.</i></b></font>

176
00:11:40,944 --> 00:11:44,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's my problem. Let's talk business.</b></font>

177
00:11:44,614 --> 00:11:46,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to race you.</b></font>

178
00:11:46,444 --> 00:11:50,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Leave tomorrow night open.</b></font>

179
00:11:50,084 --> 00:11:53,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure your engine is
fully operational by then,</b></font>

180
00:11:53,754 --> 00:11:55,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or it'll be pointless.</b></font>

181
00:11:55,994 --> 00:11:57,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I trust you.</b></font>

182
00:11:57,624 --> 00:11:59,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be in touch.</b></font>

183
00:12:12,344 --> 00:12:14,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi.</b></font>

184
00:12:14,074 --> 00:12:16,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's up?</b></font>

185
00:12:16,114 --> 00:12:18,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a favor to ask.</b></font>

186
00:12:20,184 --> 00:12:24,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may be racing the
Eight-Six Turbo tomorrow night,</b></font>

187
00:12:24,184 --> 00:12:28,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I want to make this engine usable by then.</b></font>

188
00:12:28,524 --> 00:12:32,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need your help installing a tachometer.</b></font>

189
00:12:32,024 --> 00:12:33,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A tachometer?</b></font>

190
00:12:33,924 --> 00:12:36,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know car stuff.</b></font>

191
00:12:36,194 --> 00:12:39,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no clue, so I need help.</b></font>

192
00:12:39,704 --> 00:12:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please show me how!</b></font>

193
00:12:42,234 --> 00:12:43,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

194
00:12:44,904 --> 00:12:47,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know the specifics,</b></font>

195
00:12:47,914 --> 00:12:51,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I can tell that this engine
isn't just another engine.</b></font>

196
00:12:51,744 --> 00:12:55,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--It has a good carburetor</b></font>

197
00:12:55,384 --> 00:12:58,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and a wildly twisted header.</b></font>

198
00:12:58,284 --> 00:13:00,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a new five-valve engine,</b></font>

199
00:13:00,654 --> 00:13:04,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and it's really tuned-up.</b></font>

200
00:13:04,664 --> 00:13:07,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure is hard to believe that this engine</b></font>

201
00:13:07,894 --> 00:13:09,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has less power than the old one.</b></font>

202
00:13:09,934 --> 00:13:11,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This Wataru guy</b></font>

203
00:13:11,564 --> 00:13:15,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>said that I would get
more power at a higher rpm.</b></font>

204
00:13:15,274 --> 00:13:19,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to believe what he said.</b></font>

205
00:13:19,344 --> 00:13:22,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlocking a sealed high-rev zone...</b></font>

206
00:13:22,944 --> 00:13:26,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If that's true, it's exciting.</b></font>

207
00:13:26,514 --> 00:13:30,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that hard to install a tachometer,</b></font>

208
00:13:30,854 --> 00:13:34,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but there's one thing I'm not so sure about.</b></font>

209
00:13:34,424 --> 00:13:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure you want to
change the current setup</b></font>

210
00:13:37,594 --> 00:13:40,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>without asking your dad first?</b></font>

211
00:13:42,794 --> 00:13:46,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My dad wasn't home tonight.</b></font>

212
00:13:46,804 --> 00:13:49,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And he wouldn't say yes</b></font>

213
00:13:49,374 --> 00:13:51,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if I asked him face to face.</b></font>

214
00:13:51,874 --> 00:13:54,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, I've decided to do it myself.</b></font>

215
00:13:54,774 --> 00:13:57,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to be able to use the
engine to its full potential</b></font>

216
00:13:57,984 --> 00:13:59,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by tomorrow night.</b></font>

217
00:13:59,784 --> 00:14:01,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

218
00:14:01,154 --> 00:14:04,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that case, I'll help you.</b></font>

219
00:14:04,824 --> 00:14:08,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll buy a tachometer
first thing in the morning.</b></font>

220
00:14:08,324 --> 00:14:10,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After school,</b></font>

221
00:14:10,054 --> 00:14:13,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>bring the car here as fast as you can.</b></font>

222
00:14:13,824 --> 00:14:16,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you so much, Iketani!</b></font>

223
00:14:16,164 --> 00:14:18,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a huge help.</b></font>

224
00:14:18,234 --> 00:14:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You and your Eight-Six</b></font>

225
00:14:20,064 --> 00:14:23,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>have saved my butt many times,</b></font>

226
00:14:23,074 --> 00:14:26,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so this is the least I can do.</b></font>

227
00:14:28,214 --> 00:14:30,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! It'll take a week?</b></font>

228
00:14:30,914 --> 00:14:33,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need it today.</b></font>

229
00:14:34,214 --> 00:14:36,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is bad! No one has it in stock.</b></font>

230
00:14:36,884 --> 00:14:38,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess very few cars</b></font>

231
00:14:38,384 --> 00:14:42,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>use 10,000 rpm tachometers.</b></font>

232
00:14:42,194 --> 00:14:45,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What am I going to tell Takumi?</b></font>

233
00:14:45,194 --> 00:14:47,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess no one carries it.</b></font>

234
00:14:47,364 --> 00:14:50,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss, do you know anyone?</b></font>

235
00:14:50,434 --> 00:14:54,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, maybe I do.</b></font>

236
00:14:55,774 --> 00:14:57,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

237
00:14:57,474 --> 00:15:00,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Yuichi.</b></font>

238
00:15:00,574 --> 00:15:02,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I have one.</b></font>

239
00:15:02,744 --> 00:15:06,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Are you sure you have one, Masashi?</b></font>

240
00:15:06,044 --> 00:15:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bunta asked me to get one for his Eight-Six.</b></font>

241
00:15:09,654 --> 00:15:13,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A racing tachometer, and water
temperature and oil pressure gauges.</b></font>

242
00:15:13,184 --> 00:15:14,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on.</b></font>

243
00:15:14,654 --> 00:15:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a surprise, Iketani!</b></font>

244
00:15:16,924 --> 00:15:19,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got goose bumps!</b></font>

245
00:15:19,264 --> 00:15:23,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is what Bunta meant by "sealing it."</b></font>

246
00:15:23,064 --> 00:15:27,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Masashi! Bring those
gauges over here right now!</b></font>

247
00:15:32,674 --> 00:15:35,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

248
00:15:35,344 --> 00:15:38,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's your hurry?</b></font>

249
00:15:43,354 --> 00:15:45,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mogi!</i></b></font>

250
00:15:48,194 --> 00:15:50,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hi, Takumi...</b></font>

251
00:15:54,224 --> 00:15:57,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, but I'm busy right now.</b></font>

252
00:15:57,034 --> 00:15:59,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Takumi!</b></font>

253
00:16:02,334 --> 00:16:04,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi...</i></b></font>

254
00:16:08,974 --> 00:16:10,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mogi...</i></b></font>

255
00:16:13,044 --> 00:16:16,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, now you just have to screw it down.</b></font>

256
00:16:16,584 --> 00:16:18,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's it.</b></font>

257
00:16:20,654 --> 00:16:22,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now it's done.</b></font>

258
00:16:22,654 --> 00:16:24,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wasn't that easy?</b></font>

259
00:16:24,994 --> 00:16:27,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks to you guys.</b></font>

260
00:16:27,324 --> 00:16:31,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't have known how to do it alone.</b></font>

261
00:16:31,004 --> 00:16:35,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Installing the tachometer isn't the end of it.</b></font>

262
00:16:35,374 --> 00:16:37,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just because it's a high-rev engine</b></font>

263
00:16:37,674 --> 00:16:40,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>doesn't mean that it'll rev infinitely.</b></font>

264
00:16:40,174 --> 00:16:44,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Without knowing its top rpm,</b></font>

265
00:16:44,014 --> 00:16:46,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can't have a full-blast race.</b></font>

266
00:16:46,544 --> 00:16:48,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure your dad knows.</b></font>

267
00:16:48,684 --> 00:16:50,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't know its limit,</b></font>

268
00:16:50,514 --> 00:16:54,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you may end up damaging this engine.</b></font>

269
00:16:54,694 --> 00:16:56,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My dad.</b></font>

270
00:17:00,724 --> 00:17:02,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't that...?</b></font>

271
00:17:14,004 --> 00:17:16,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like you're ready.</b></font>

272
00:17:16,644 --> 00:17:19,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll race tonight as planned.</b></font>

273
00:17:19,984 --> 00:17:23,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll let you pick the course for our race.</b></font>

274
00:17:23,714 --> 00:17:26,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Haven't we seen that Eight-Six Turbo before?</b></font>

275
00:17:26,824 --> 00:17:30,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, and he's Itsuki's girlfriend's brother.</b></font>

276
00:17:30,494 --> 00:17:33,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! That sounds very complicated.</b></font>

277
00:17:33,494 --> 00:17:36,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, that's fine.</b></font>

278
00:17:36,494 --> 00:17:38,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll see you there.</b></font>

279
00:17:38,664 --> 00:17:40,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Later.</b></font>

280
00:17:49,844 --> 00:17:52,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, where are you two racing?</b></font>

281
00:17:52,844 --> 00:17:55,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll come root for you.</b></font>

282
00:17:54,854 --> 00:17:57,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Matsuya Inn"</b></font>

283
00:17:58,854 --> 00:18:00,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother!</b></font>

284
00:18:00,254 --> 00:18:03,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is serious.</b></font>

285
00:18:03,224 --> 00:18:06,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you not to make our aunt look bad.</b></font>

286
00:18:06,794 --> 00:18:09,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You made Mom and Dad worry.</b></font>

287
00:18:09,894 --> 00:18:14,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get your stuff together tonight.
I'm taking you home.</b></font>

288
00:18:14,804 --> 00:18:17,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's my decision to make!</b></font>

289
00:18:17,804 --> 00:18:22,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was wrong to stay out till morning
without letting anyone know.</b></font>

290
00:18:22,514 --> 00:18:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I did nothing I'm ashamed of,</b></font>

291
00:18:25,984 --> 00:18:28,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I shouldn't have to go home!</b></font>

292
00:18:28,314 --> 00:18:30,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you explain that</b></font>

293
00:18:30,814 --> 00:18:33,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to Mom and Dad instead of me?</b></font>

294
00:18:33,654 --> 00:18:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you like it here,</b></font>

295
00:18:35,654 --> 00:18:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can tell them so and come back.</b></font>

296
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:42,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can tell you've changed a little,</b></font>

297
00:18:42,864 --> 00:18:44,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I have to admit</b></font>

298
00:18:44,864 --> 00:18:48,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that you've even matured a little.</b></font>

299
00:18:48,234 --> 00:18:51,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But they don't know that, so they worry.</b></font>

300
00:18:51,574 --> 00:18:55,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll feel better if they hear it from you.</b></font>

301
00:18:56,574 --> 00:18:59,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I'll go.</b></font>

302
00:18:59,384 --> 00:19:02,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Takeuchi"</b></font>

303
00:19:00,814 --> 00:19:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

304
00:19:02,514 --> 00:19:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm racing tonight.</b></font>

305
00:19:05,324 --> 00:19:08,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! With who?</b></font>

306
00:19:08,024 --> 00:19:11,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not with Kazumi's brother?</b></font>

307
00:19:11,224 --> 00:19:15,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, and I have a favor to ask.</b></font>

308
00:19:15,694 --> 00:19:19,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm a little scared, so can you come with me?</b></font>

309
00:19:19,234 --> 00:19:21,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, of course.</b></font>

310
00:19:21,574 --> 00:19:24,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks. I'll pick you up later.</b></font>

311
00:19:50,434 --> 00:19:52,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it?</b></font>

312
00:19:52,564 --> 00:19:56,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm racing in this car tonight.</b></font>

313
00:19:56,734 --> 00:19:58,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It has a new tachometer.</b></font>

314
00:19:58,874 --> 00:20:01,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please tell me what the top rpm is.</b></font>

315
00:20:03,014 --> 00:20:04,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please.</b></font>

316
00:20:21,234 --> 00:20:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure to rev up to 11,000 rpm.</b></font>

317
00:20:25,404 --> 00:20:27,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't lose.</b></font>

318
00:20:36,274 --> 00:20:39,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks, Dad.</b></font>

319
00:20:41,754 --> 00:20:45,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, why are we taking the highway?</b></font>

320
00:20:45,654 --> 00:20:49,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He told me to pick any course I wanted.</b></font>

321
00:20:49,494 --> 00:20:52,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, where did you pick?</b></font>

322
00:20:52,164 --> 00:20:54,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shomaru Pass.</b></font>

323
00:20:54,164 --> 00:20:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! That's his turf!</b></font>

324
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

325
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was always that</i>
<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

326
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was there on days when</i>
<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

327
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And even on days with a little happiness in them</i></b></font>

328
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My hands aren't enough</i></b></font>

329
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To hold on to all the love you gave me</i></b></font>

330
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The warm wind</i></b></font>

331
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Comes back quietly and tenderly</i></b></font>

332
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And as I gaze at the sky alone</i></b></font>

333
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You smile down upon me</i></b></font>

334
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are still waving to me from the radiant light</i></b></font>

335
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like you did that day</i></b></font>

336
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are my everlasting memory</i></b></font>

